@node GETMARKEDFILE
@toc File
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
       GetMarkedFile

   SYNOPSIS
       GetMarkedFile <FIRST | LAST | NEXT | PREVIOUS>

   FUNCTION
       Traverse the current users list of marked files.
       If a marked file is correctly loaded, its information
       can be displayed using the CC file commands (%10xx|).

   INPUTS
