@node PAGELIST
@toc File
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
       PageList

   SYNOPSIS
       PageList [JUMP] [CONTINUOUS] [AGAIN]

   FUNCTION
       Outputs a file list, as defined by ARexx/SimpleList and
       the folling Language strings:

       FILEFORMAT:
       SCANAREAS:
       FIRSTFILE:
       STDINDENT:
       STDFILENAME:

       SHORTLIST:
       ENDLIST:

       See the example languages and CC list for more information.

   INPUTS
       JUMP        -- move to next file area
       CONTINUOUS  -- list files without stopping
       AGAIN       -- currently unimplemented

   RESULT

   RC
       0 -- Finished
       1 -- End of page. Call PageList again to continue
       2 -- Done all (wanted) files in area
       3 -- In continuous mode, user broke output by pressing a key

   EXAMPLE

   NOTES

   SEE ALSO
       @{"SimpleList" link "SimpleList"} @{"EndList" link "EndList"}

@rem </PRE>
@endnode

