@node "Mailer.BANNER"
@toc Mailer
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
       Banner

   SYNOPSIS
       Banner '"<TEXT|FILE>"'

   FUNCTION
       A line of text always displayed to the user when they connect. The `|'
       character is replaced by a newline. If the first character of this text
       is a `<', then a textfile is displayed, e.g. putting
       `@{i}<Zeus:Text/Banner.txt@{ui}' would display
       @{i}Zeus:Text/Banner.txt@{ui} on connect.

   INPUTS
       TEXT|FILE -- the text or filename to display.

   RESULT

   RC

   EXAMPLE

   NOTES

   SEE ALSO

@rem </PRE>
@endnode

