@node pnxrexx.PnxGetExtractStr                             pnxrexx.PnxGetExtractStr
@toc Phoenix
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
      PnxGetExtractStr

   SYNOPSIS
      PnxGetExtractStr <arcno>

   FUNCTION
      Returns the extract string of archiver <arcno>. In the string
      there should be a ~a. You should place the name of the file
      to extract here.

   NOTES

   INPUTS
      ArcNo    A number of an archiver in Zeus' configuration.

   RESULT
      RC  0 Ok, the extract string should be in RESULT.
      RC  5 Bad arguments.
      RC 11 Couldn't find archiver.

