@rem </PRE>
@endnode

@node pnxrexx.PnxGetPnxConfig                               pnxrexx.PnxGetPnxConfig
@toc Phoenix
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
      PnxGetPnxConfig

   SYNOPSIS
      PnxGetPnxConfig <BBSID|PHONENO|HELLO|GOODBYE|NEWS|FILELIST|WORK|
                       MAXPKT|MAXAREA|ZONE|NET|NODE|POINT>

   FUNCTION
      Returns information from Phoenix's own configuration.

   NOTES

   INPUTS
      BbsId    BBS Id.
      PhoneNo  Phone number to the BBS.
      Hello    Full path to the hello file.
      Goodbye  Full path to the goodbye file.
      News     Full path to the news file.
      Filelist Full path to the new files list.
      Work     Work path.
      MaxPkt   Limit of how many messages that can be dumped pr packet.
      MaxArea  Limit of how many messages that can be dumped pr conference.
      Zone     BBS primary Zone number.
      Net      BBS primary Net number.
      Node     BBS primary Node number.
      Point    BBS primary Point number.

   RESULT
      RC  0 The requested information is in RESULT.
      RC  5 Bad arguments
      RC 11 Couldn't load Phoenix's configuration.

   BUGS

   SEE ALSO

@rem </PRE>
@endnode

