@node pnxrexx.PnxMaskArea                                       pnxrexx.PnxMaskArea
@toc Phoenix
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
      PnxMaskArea

   SYNOPSIS
      PnxMaskArea <area> [GET|IN|OUT]

   FUNCTION
      Masks in or out an area, or tells if an area is masked out (resigned).
      If RESULT is 1 the area is masked out.

   NOTES

   INPUTS
      area  Number of area.
      GET   Is area masked out?
      IN    Mask area in (join).
      OUT   Mask area out (resign).

   RESULT
      RC  0 Ok/Info is in RESULT.
      RC  1 Mask in/out failed.
      RC  5 Bad arguments
      RC 10 Couldn't get line.
      RC 11 Area doesn't exists.

   BUGS

   SEE ALSO

@rem </PRE>
@endnode

