@toc AlphaIndex
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
       InitLine -- Initialises the line.

   SYNOPSIS
       InitLine

   FUNCTION
       General function for initializing the line after a call.  This
       function should be put at the top of EVERY StartUp#.zeus script
       (the script specified with BBSLine as the one to run when the
       line is started).

