@node NICELINE
@toc AlphaIndex
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
       NiceLine -- Formats a string neatly.

   SYNOPSIS
       NiceLine '"<String>"'

   FUNCTION
       Formats a line of text nicely, removing excess spaces etc.

   INPUTS
       String -- The text to be reformatted.

   RESULT
       The reformatted text.

   RC
        0 -- Successful
       10 -- Bad args.

   EXAMPLE

       NiceLine '"  hello from Zeus. "'

       RESULT then equals '"hello from Zeus."'

