@toc AlphaIndex
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
       NiceName -- Formats a name neatly.

   SYNOPSIS
       NiceName '"<Name>"'

   FUNCTION
       Formats a name neatly, similarly to NiceLine, but makes some
       intellegent decisions when encountering names such as
       "McKenna."  Strips spaces and capitalises.

   INPUTS
       Name -- The text to be reformatted/capitalised.

   RESULT
       The reformatted name.

   RC
        0 -- Successful
       10 -- Bad args.

   EXAMPLE

       NiceName '" dimitry herbert-smythe "'

       RESULT then equals '"Dimitry Herbert-Smythe"'

   NOTES
       Asynchronous

   SEE ALSO
       @{"NiceLine" link "NiceLine"}

@rem </PRE>
@endnode

