@node PUSHINPUT
@toc AlphaIndex
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
       PushInput -- Push text into the BBS.

   SYNOPSIS
       PushInput '"<String>"'

   FUNCTION
       Writes <String> on the BBS exactly as if the user had typed
       it in.  Next time any script on the BBS issues a command
       which requires input, the string given here will be passed
       on to it.

   INPUTS
       String  -- the text to push.

   RESULT

   RC
        0 -- Input placed in the stream.
       10 -- Bad arguments.
       20 -- Fatal Error. (No user online)

   EXAMPLE

