@toc AlphaIndex
@rem <PRE>

   NAME
       PutOnline -- Puts a user online.

   SYNOPSIS
       PutOnline '<User>'

   FUNCTION
       Places <User> online.  Normally and must be used in Logon
       scripts.

   INPUTS
       User -- A user key as returns by LoadUser.

   RESULT

   RC
        0 -- Successful
        5 -- User was not placed online, invalid key.
       10 -- Bad args.

   EXAMPLE

